package com.example.util

/**
 * Adds the given [element] to this mutable collection.
 *
 * @receiver the collection to which the element will be added
 * @param element the element to add
 * @return `true` if the collection changed as a result of the call
 *
 * This helper shields callers from having to remember whether a collection is mutable
